ry parameter -->\n| released             = <!-- {{Start date|YYYY|MM|DD}} -->\n| first_aired          = {{Start date|2020|02|25}}\n| last_aired           = <!-- {{End date|YYYY|MM|DD}} -->\n| preceded_by          = \n| followed_by          = \n| related              = \n| website              = \n| website_title        = \n| production_website   = \n| production_website_title = \n}}\n\n'''''Hungry Sister''''' (known in its original [[Thai language]] as ''Hungry Sister'' {{lang|th|\u0e1e\u0e35\u0e48\u0e2a\u0e32\u0e27\u0e09\u0e31\u0e19\u0e2b\u0e34\u0e27}}) is a [[Thailand|Thai]] [[web series]] of [[GMMTV]] hosted by [[Watchara Sukchum]] (Jennie Panhan) and [[Tawan Vihokratana]] (Tay) currently available for streaming on [[YouTube]] and [[Facebook Watch]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Hungry Sister \u0e1e\u0e35\u0e48\u0e2a\u0e32\u0e27\u0e09\u0e31\u0e19\u0e2b\u0e34\u0e27 Youtube Playlist |url=https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLszepnkojZI7NjPwYY4TmeXWO-Dln9lxq |website=youtube.com |publisher=[[GMMTV]] |accessdate=3 April 2020}}</ref>\n\nEach episode features different places where ''Tay'' introduces one of his friends to ''Jennie'' as they enjoy a meal together. The series premiered on February 25, 2020 and airs every 2nd and 4th Tuesday of the month.<ref>{{cite web |title=\u0e44\u0e21\u0e48\u0e40\u0e2a\u0e35\u0e22\u0e0a\u0e37\u0e48\u0e2d! '\u0e40\u0e15' \u0e19\u0e31\u0e14\u0e40\u0e14\u0e17\u0e2a\u0e38\u0e14\u0e0b\u0e35\u0e49\u0e14\u0e43\u0e2b\u0e49 '\u0e40\u0e08\u0e19\u0e19\u0e35\u0e48' \u0e01\u0e31\u0e1a \u0e2b\u0e19\u0e38\u0e48\u0e21\u0e08\u0e38\u0e2c\u0e32\u0e2f\u0e04\u0e17\u0e32\u0e01\u0e23 - Hungry Sister \u0e1e\u0e35\u0e48\u0e2a\u0e32\u0e27\u0e09\u0e31\u0e19\u0e2b\u0e34\u0e27 EP.1 |url=https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2482094475377544 |website=facebook.com |publisher=[[GMMTV]] |accessdate=3 April 2020 |date=25 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n== Episodes ==\n{{Episode table|background=#092a81 |total_width=68 |overall=1 |airdate=1 |aux2=5 |aux2T=Guest |aux4=1 |aux4T={{abbr|