-stars-in-new-weezer-video-for-a-has-take-on-me.html|title=CALPURNIA STARS IN NEW WEEZER VIDEO FOR a ha's \"TAKE ON ME\"|website=Music News Net|access-date=February 13, 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== Audiobooks ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|+ \n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Role\n! scope=\"col\" | Author\n! scope=\"col\"| Notes\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | Refs\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |'''2020'''\n| ''When You Finish Saving the World''\n| Ziggy\n| [[Jesse Eisenberg]]\n| An [[Audible_(store)|Audible]] Original\n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/04/julianne-moore-finn-wolfhard-star-jesse-eisenberg-comedy-when-you-finish-saving-world-with-emma-stone-producing-1202903425/|title=Hot Project Du Jour: Julianne Moore & Finn Wolfhard To Star In Jesse Eisenberg-Directed \u2018When You Finish Saving The World\u2019 Based On Audible Original; Emma Stone Producing|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=April 9, 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== Discography ==\n{{Main|Calpurnia (band)}}\n\n===Extended plays===\n'''With the Aubreys'''\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\n!Title\n!Details\n|-\n|''Soda & Pie''\n|Release: 13 March 2020<br>\n{{Hlist|Label: [[AWAL]] {{small|(US/CA/UK/EU)}}}} Format: Digital download, streaming\n|}\n\n===Singles===\n'''With the Aubreys'''\n* \"Loved One\" (2020)\n* \"Getting Better (Otherwise)\" (2020)\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Nominated work\n! Result\n! {{Abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2017\n| [[38th Young Artist Awards|Young Artist Awards]]\n| [[38th Young Artist Awards#Best Performance in a Digital TV Series or Film|Best Performance in a Digital TV Series or Film&nbsp;\u2013 Teen Actor]]\n| rowspan=\"5\"| ''[[Stranger Things (TV series)|Stranger Things]]''\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref name=\"2016YAA\">{{cite web|title=38th Annual Awards |url=http://www.youngartistawards.org/noms25.htm |publisher=[[Young Artist Associati